text: Magnum Force is a 1973 American action movie directed by Ted Post. It stars Clint Eastwood, Hal Holbrook, and Mitchell Ryan. It is the first sequel to Dirty Harry. It was released to positive reviews on December 25, 1973. == Other websites == * Category:1973 crime movies Category:American action movies Category:American crime movies Category:American serial killer movies Category:Movies set in San Francisco Category:Sequel movies Category:1973 action movies Category:Movies directed by Ted Post
